                                          FLIGHT MANAGER APPLICATION

This application serves as a flight manager simulator. 
Applications allows you to create (or choose) an airport, an airline, flight and also book a seat for created (chosen) flight. 
There are some conditions that need to be satisfied in order to create a flight :
 - name of airport must have exactly three alphabetical characters,
 -two airports can't have same name 
 - airline must have name which length isn't greater than six alphabetical characters. 
 - no two airlines can have the same name. Seats are organized in rows.
  Each row has number of seats and it's marked with a letter ("A", "B", "C", "D", "E", "F"). These conditions are set in methods. 
They are checking the inputs and if all conditions are satisfied, you have successfully created your trip.